reviewText: The dvd skips and is fuzzy
I REAL LIKE THIS DVD, IT HAS GREAT MATCH AND GREAT OLD SCHOOL WRESTLING!! I SAY A MUST HAVE.
Nice DVD of primarily Memphis wrestling  1st Half mostly studio matches with 2nd half mostly mid south coliseum matches
i am very pleased with this dvd thanks

Can understand why it is selling so well. Great DVD, rare Lawler vs Rich Match. Also good quality and nice mix if matches. This is a winner if you like Southern Wrestling. All the top names are here Gilbert, Mantell, Armstrong, DWB's and so many more. 22 matches and a Lawler feud recap by Jerry himself. Nice DVD
